thread.title: Joanna Zhang

author: Joanna Zhang
title: Joanna Zhang
text: Servcorp holds various locations in the world and keeps the integrity for the service. Last time I went to UK and got a beautiful day suite for free as part of my package. The special thing is my local office in Norwest are always friendly and professional, they always try to deliver the best support and service. Especially thanks to the manager Brooke and secretory Kiarnie. Feel lovely to be part of Servcorp!!!
